<doc id="970890" wikidata="Q6465937" url="?curid=970890" title="La Woz">
<text>La Woz (Antillean Creole for &quot;The Rose&quot;) is one of the two historic cultural societies (&quot;sociétés&quot;) of the Antillean country of Saint Lucia. It is also the name of the society&#x27;s festival, held every August. The other &quot;societé&quot; is &quot;La Magwit&quot; (&quot;The Marguerite&quot;), which holds its festival in October.</text><links>
